Attribution
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Portions of the BLE control protocol (input map, master-volume range, and the
percent conversion math) are aligned with the hardware-confirmed Linux
"fives-api" project by ssalaues (MIT-licensed):

    https://github.com/ssalaues/fives-api

The remaining protocol details (EQ, mute, sound modes, transport, rename, model
detection via the Device Information Service) were independently reverse
engineered for interoperability from the official "Klipsch Connect"
(com.klipsch.connect) application.

